FLEX BOX

CSS3 layout mode that provides an easy and clean way to arrange items with a container

Display Flex - using display flex in "parent elements", child elements automatically align like columns or rows with auto width and auto height

MEDIA QUERIES

min-width: 768px - from bigger screen to small the content is showing flex items until it reach 768px it will not show
max-width: 768px - from bigger screen to small the content will not change until you reach 768px


/// FLEX PROPERTIES ///
display: flex | inline-flex | block

flex-direction: row | column
row will assign items horizontally
column will assign items vertically

flex-wrap: wrap | nowrap | wrapreverse

flex-basis: <length>

justify-content: flex-start | flex-end | center

align-self: flex-start | flex-end | center

align-items: flex-start | flex-end | center

align content: flex start | flex-end | center

flex-grow: <number>;

flex-shrink: <number>;

flex: <integer>;

order: <integer>;

